OL,7,FWhen the batteries are improperly
OL,8,Fcharged or exposed to high heat, they
OL,9,Fcan overheat and cause fires or
OL,10,Fexplosions.
OL,12,FWhat are the key causes of lithium-ion
OL,13,Fbattery incidents?
OL,15,FCouncillor Andy Crump, portfolio
OL,16,Fholder for Community Safety and Fire
OL,17,Fsaid: "Lithium-ion batteries are a
OL,18,Fpart of modern life, but they come
OL,19,Fwith risks that can lead to
OL,20,Fdevastating consequences.
