OL,5,CWarwickshire
OL,7,F"We want to raise awareness about the
OL,8,Fsteps people can take to safely use
OL,9,Fthese types of batteries and
OL,10,Funderstanding how to use, charge, and
OL,11,Fdispose of them is essential to
OL,12,Fpreventing fires and protecting lives.
OL,14,F"The increase in incidents in both
OL,15,FWarwickshire and the UK highlights the
OL,16,Fneed for awareness so that we can keep
OL,17,Fourselves safe as technology and
OL,18,Fappliances continue to evolve.
